snippet.title: Resistor - First Look Gameplay Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10008635

RESISTOR is a turbocharged narrative-driven adventure RPG featuring open-world exploration, stunt-infused racing, and explosive vehicular combat! Build up your team and unravel a twisting story as you compete to take down an oppressive mega-corporation and its enigmatic director. 

Take a first look at the how this ‘CARPG’ blends cinematic storytelling with arcade style racing as rising star Aster comes face to face with a dangerous new adversary. Design your own racer, customise your ride, and reconfigure your plasma engine before hitting the track to dominate your rivals and master increasingly more hazardous environments! 

Coming soon to PlayStation 5, wishlist now!

#ps5 #ps5games
